title: A conference devoted to register and big data opens today (SE - Statistics Estonia)
text: ( Source : SE - Statistics Estonia ) The conference is held on the World Statistics Day , which is celebrated under the aegis of the UN on 20 October . The slogan of the World Statistics Day - better data, better lives - is the theme running
